_sText: This map is based in a large prison. One bomb site is in the laundry room and the other is in the cafeteria. There are many different routes around the map. I created custom decals to mark the way to the bomb sites. The map is best when players work together to defend or assault the bomb sites. More screen shots are avalible at my web site. -www.rickets007.com- de_cellblock_f
